sequenceDiagram
    participant MCP as "MCP Server<br/>(index.ts)"
    participant Client as "AutoMemClient<br/>(automem-client.ts)"
    participant API as "AutoMem API"
    participant Qdrant as "Qdrant<br/>(vectors)"
    participant FalkorDB as "FalkorDB<br/>(graph)"
    
    Note over MCP: recall_memory handler<br/>checks for tags
    
    alt Tags Present
        par Parallel Queries
            MCP->>Client: recallMemory(args)
            Client->>API: GET /recall?query=...&tags=...
            activate API
            API->>Qdrant: Semantic search
            API->>FalkorDB: Tag + keyword filter
            API-->>Client: Primary results
            deactivate API
        and
            MCP->>Client: searchByTag({tags})
            Client->>API: GET /memory/by-tag?tags=...
            activate API
            API->>FalkorDB: Tag-only query
            API-->>Client: Tag-only results
            deactivate API
        end
        
        Note over MCP: Merge results<br/>Deduplicate by memory_id
        MCP->>MCP: Sort by final_score
        MCP->>MCP: Enforce limit
    else No Tags
        MCP->>Client: recallMemory(args)
        Client->>API: GET /recall?query=...
        API->>Qdrant: Semantic search
        API->>FalkorDB: Keyword filter
        API-->>Client: Results
    end